				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${p}_{max}$$\end{document}. The current and voltage ripples refer to the corresponding peak-to-peak values. The following equations are used to calculate the errors of the five different techniques and n is defined as the number of data points.

